job-description-los-vaq-associate = You are either a recruit or associate of the Los Vaqueros Cartel. Do your best to follow orders.
job-description-los-vaq-falcon = You are a trusted, and potentially hardened, errand runner of the Los Vaqueros Cartel. Do your best to follow orders.
job-description-los-vaq-enforcer = You are a proven foot soldier of the Los Vaqueros Cartel. Do your best to follow orders and collect what you can from those less powerful, either in strength or willpower. 
job-description-los-vaq-underboss = You are a high ranking member of the Los Vaqueros Cartel. You are to accept orders and delegate them to those under your command. Remember, you earned this position in some way that likely involved doing things others didn't have the stomach for.
job-description-los-vaq-boss = You are in charge of the cartel in this area. Do your absolute best to materially benefit from those less powerful than you and your men.
